OL,3,CInfrastructure Minister wants to
OL,4,Cdelist parts of former St Saviour's
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FInfrastructure Minister has told ITV
OL,8,FNews he wants to look at delisting
OL,9,Fparts of the former St Saviour's
OL,10,Fmental health hospital.
OL,12,FConstable Andy Jehan is proposing to
OL,13,Fkeep the facade, but delist other
OL,14,Fparts that are making the building
OL,15,Fharder to redevelop.
