OL,3,CInfrastructure Minister wants to
OL,4,Cdelist parts of former St Saviour's
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,FHe said: "I don't think many people
OL,8,Fhave happy memories from this
OL,9,Fbuilding, but it's an asset of the
OL,10,Fisland and we need to make sure we
OL,11,Fmake the best use of this asset. My
OL,12,Fpersonal view is I would knock it all
OL,13,Fdown.
OL,15,F"If you look at this site as a whole,
OL,16,Fit's absolutely massive. Whether we
OL,17,Fuse it for affordable homes and or
OL,18,Fhealth is under discussion, but we've
OL,19,Fjust got to get on and find a solution.
