OL,3,CInfrastructure Minister wants to
OL,4,Cdelist parts of former St Saviour's
OL,5,CHospital
OL,7,F"We need to make it work for us and if
OL,8,Fthat means delisting part of it, then
OL,9,FI very much support that. "
OL,11,FConstable Jehan is also looking to
OL,12,Fsell government buildings that are no
OL,13,Flonger viable to keep.
OL,15,FHe explained: "We need to look at not
OL,16,Fonly buildings, but also land. We've
OL,17,Fgot some land that becomes a liability
OL,18,Ffor us as a government, but we should
OL,19,Falso be looking at acquiring land that
OL,20,Fwould be an asset for the island.
